定义URL或其他内容类型。在下方左栏中展开的框中选择项目可添加菜单链接。','Menu Management'=>'菜单管理','You can assign theme locations to individual menus by <strong>selecting the desired settings</strong> at the bottom of the menu editor. To assign menus to all theme locations at once, <strong>visit the Manage Locations tab</strong> at the top of the screen.'=>'要指派单独菜单的主题位置，您可在菜单编辑器的底部<strong>选择想要的设置</strong>。要指派菜单到所有主题位置，请在顶部<strong>访问“管理位置”页</strong>。','If you haven&#8217;t yet created any menus, <strong>click the &#8217;create a new menu&#8217; link</strong> to get started'=>'如果您还没有创建任何菜单，请<strong>点击“创建新菜单”链接</strong>来开始','To edit an existing menu, <strong>choose a menu from the drop down and click Select</strong>'=>'要编辑已存在的菜单，<strong>在下拉菜单中选择菜单并点击“选择”</strong>','The menu management box at the top of the screen is used to control which menu is opened in the editor below.'=>'顶部的菜单管理框可用来控制在下方编辑器中打开哪个菜单。','Add, organize, and modify individual menu items'=>'添加、管理和修改某一菜单项','Create, edit, and delete menus'=>'创建、编辑和删除菜单','From this screen you can:'=>'在此界面中，您可以：','Menus can be displayed in locations defined by your theme, even used in sidebars by adding a &#8220;Navigation Menu&#8221; widget on the <a href="%1$s">Widgets</a> screen. If your theme does not support the navigation menus feature (the default themes, %2$s and %3$s, do), you can learn about adding this support by following the Documentation link to the side.'=>'菜单可在您的主题指定的位置显示，或通过<a href="%1$s">小工具</a>中的“导航菜单”小工具显示在侧栏中。如果您的主题不支持导航菜单功能（默认主题%2$s和%3$s均支持），您可以查阅侧面的文档链接了解如何加入这一支持。','This screen is used for managing your navigation menus.'=>'此界面用于管理您的导航菜单。','Your theme does not natively support menus, but you can use them in sidebars by adding a &#8220;Navigation Menu&#8221; widget on the <a href="%s">Widgets</a> screen.'=>'当前的主题未提供原生的菜单支持，您可以通过在<a href="%s">小工具</a>添加“导航菜单”小工具来在侧栏上显示。','Menu locations updated.'=>'菜单位置已更新。','Please enter a valid menu name.'=>'请输入有效的菜单名称。','Selected menus have been successfully deleted.'=>'菜单已被成功删除。','The menu has been successfully deleted.'=>'菜单已被成功删除。','The menu item has been successfully deleted.'=>'菜单项已被成功删除。','Your theme does not support navigation menus or widgets.'=>'您的主题不支持导航菜单或小工具。','If you absolutely have to make direct edits to this plugin, use a file manager to create a copy with a new name and hang on to the original. That way, you can re-enable a functional version if something goes wrong.'=>'如果您必须直接修改此插件，请使用资源管理器将文件复制一份并保留修改前的版本。这样当出现问题时您就能恢复到正常的版本。','You appear to be making direct edits to your plugin in the WordPress dashboard. We recommend that you don&#8217;t! Editing plugins directly may introduce incompatibilities that break your site and your changes may be lost in future updates.'=>'看起来您正在WordPress仪表盘中直接编辑您的插件。我们不推荐这样做！直接编辑您的插件可能会损害您的站点，您的修改也可能在将来的更新中灭失。','<strong>Warning:</strong> Making changes to active plugins is not recommended.'=>'<strong>警告：</strong>不推荐修改已启用的插件。','Plugin Files'=>'插件文件','Select plugin to edit:'=>'选择要编辑的插件：','Browsing %s (inactive)'=>'正在浏览%s（未启用）','Editing %s (inactive)'=>'正在编辑%s（未启用）','Browsing %s (active)'=>'正在浏览%s（已启用）','Editing %s (active)'=>'正在编辑%s（已启用）','<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/plugins/">Documentation on Writing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/plugins/">编写插件文档</a>','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-editor-screen/">Documentation on Editing Plugins</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/article/plugins-editor-screen/">编辑插件文档</a>','If you want to make changes but don&#8217;t want them to be overwritten when the plugin is updated, you may be ready to think about writing your own plugin. For information on how to edit plugins, write your own from scratch, or just better understand their anatomy, check out the links below.'=>'若您不希望您所做的修改因插件升级而被覆盖，请考虑自己编写插件。右侧的链接提供了自行制作插件的一些方法和指导。','The Documentation menu below the editor lists the PHP functions recognized in the plugin file. Clicking Look Up takes you to a web page about that particular function.'=>'“文档”菜单列出了我们从该文件中找到的所有函数。点击“查询”按钮可查看有关该函数的页面。','Choose a plugin to edit from the dropdown menu and click the Select button. Click once on any file name to load it in the editor, and make your changes. Don&#8217;t forget to save your changes (Update File) when you&#8217;re finished.'=>'请从下拉菜单中选择要编辑的插件，然后点选您希望编辑的文件。在编辑完成后，请您不要忘记保存（点击“更新文件”按钮）。','You can use the plugin editor to make changes to any of your plugins&#8217; individual PHP files. Be aware that if you make changes, plugins updates will overwrite your customizations.'=>'您可以使用插件编辑器来编辑插件的PHP文件。请注意，如果您做出修改，插件更新后将会覆盖这些修改。','Edit Plugins'=>'编辑插件','Search Requests'=>'搜索请求','Send Request'=>'发送请求','Username or email address'=>'用户名或电子邮件地址','An email will be sent to the user at this email address asking them to verify the request.'=>'一份电子邮件将被发往此电子邮件地址来确认此请求。','Add Data Erasure Request'=>'加入数据抹除请求','Erase personal data list'=>'抹除个人数据列表','Erase personal data list navigation'=>'抹除个人数据列表导航','Filter erase personal data list'=>'过滤抹除个人数据列表','Sorry, you are not allowed to erase personal data on this site.'=>'抱歉，您不能抹除此站点的个人数据。','WordPress has been installed. Thank you, and enjoy!'=>'WordPress安装完成。谢谢！','Success!'=>'成功！','Sorry, that isn&#8217;t a valid email address. Email addresses look like <code>username@example.com</code>.'=>'抱歉，电子邮件地址无效。形如<code>username@example.com</code>的才是电子邮件地址。','You must provide an email address.'=>'您必须提供电子邮件地址。','Your passwords do not match. Please try again.'=>'您两次输入的密码不符，请重试。','The username you provided has invalid characters.'=>'您提供的用户名包含非法字符。','Please provide a valid username.'=>'请提供有效的用户名。','Please provide the following information. Don&#8217;t worry, you can always change these settings later.'=>'您需要填写一些基本信息。无需担心填错，这些信息以后可以再次修改。','Information needed'=>'需要信息','Welcome to the famous five-minute WordPress installation process! Just fill in the information below and you&#8217;ll be on your way to using the most extendable and powerful personal publishing platform in the world.'=>'欢迎使用著名的WordPress五分钟安装程序！请简单地填写下面的表格，来开始