ublish'=>'剪裁并发布','You need JavaScript to choose a part of the image.'=>'您需要JavaScript支持以选择图像的一部分。','Choose the part of the image you want to use as your header.'=>'从图像中选取一部分作为您的页面顶部图像。','Crop Header Image'=>'剪裁顶部图像','Image Processing Error'=>'图像处理发生错误','Image could not be processed. Please go back and try again.'=>'无法处理图像。请返回重试。','The current theme does not support uploading a custom header image.'=>'当前主题不支持上传自定义的头部图像。','colorDefault: %s'=>'默认色：%s','Show header text with your image.'=>'将顶部文字和图像一并显示。','Restore Original Header Image'=>'重设顶部图像','This will restore the original header image. You will not be able to restore any customizations.'=>'这将重设顶部图像。之后，您将无法还原任何自定义元素。','Reset Image'=>'重置图像','Remove Header Image'=>'移除顶部图像','This will remove the header image. You will not be able to restore any customizations.'=>'这将移除顶部图像。之后，您将无法还原任何自定义元素。','You can use one of these cool headers or show a random one on each page.'=>'您可现在从这些精美的顶部图像中选择，或让WordPress在每次显示页面时随机挑选。','If you don&lsquo;t want to upload your own image, you can use one of these cool headers, or show a random one.'=>'若您现在不想上传您自己的图像，可从这些精美的顶部图像中选择，或让WordPress在每次显示页面时随机挑选。','Default Images'=>'默认图像','You can choose one of your previously uploaded headers, or show a random one.'=>'您可以从上传过的顶部图像中选择，或让WordPress在每次显示页面时随机挑选。','Uploaded Images'=>'已上传的图像','Set as header'=>'设为顶部','Choose a Custom Header'=>'选择自定义顶部','Suggested height is %s.'=>'推荐高度为%s。','Suggested width is %s.'=>'推荐宽度为%s。','Images should be at least %s tall.'=>'图片高度应至少为%s。','%d pixels'=>'%d像素','Images should be at least %s wide.'=>'图片宽度应至少为%s。','Images of exactly <strong>%1$d &times; %2$d pixels</strong> will be used as-is.'=>'使用图像的<strong>%1$d &times; %2$d像素</strong>。','You can select an image to be shown at the top of your site by uploading from your computer or choosing from your media library. After selecting an image you will be able to crop it.'=>'在这里，您可以上传新图片或从媒体库中已上传的图像中选择，以取代默认的图像。上传完成后，您将可以按喜好自己剪裁图像。','Header updated. <a href="%s">Visit your site</