'Some themes come with additional header images bundled. If you see multiple images displayed, select the one you&#8217;d like and click the &#8220;Save Changes&#8221; button.'=>'一些主题附带了更多顶部图像供您选择。若显示了多幅图像，请选择您喜爱的图像并点击“保存更改”。','You can set a custom image header for your site. Simply upload the image and crop it, and the new header will go live immediately. Alternatively, you can use an image that has already been uploaded to your Media Library by clicking the &#8220;Choose Image&#8221; button.'=>'您可为站点选择一个自定义顶部图像。只需上传需要的图像并进行剪裁，新顶部图像将会立即生效。或者您也可以点击“选择图像”，使用“媒体库”中原来上传过的图像。','You can choose from the theme&#8217;s default header images, or use one of your own. You can also customize how your Site Title and Tagline are displayed.'=>'您可以从主题默认的顶部图像中选择，或使用您自己准备的顶部图像。您还可以定义“站点标题”和“副标题”的显示方式。','This screen is used to customize the header section of your theme.'=>'在本页面调整主题顶部的样式。','A test is unavailable'=>'测试不可用','The loopback request to your site completed successfully.'=>'到您站点的环回请求成功完成。','The loopback request returned an unexpected http status code, %d, it was not possible to determine if this will prevent features from working as expected.'=>'到您站点的环回请求返回了预期外的HTTP状态码%d，无法判断依赖此种请求的功能是否能正常工作。','The loopback request to your site failed, this means features relying on them are not currently working as expected.'=>'到您站点的环回请求失败，这意味着依赖此种请求的功能将不能正常工作。','There appear to be no issues with plugin and theme auto-updates.'=>'插件和主题自动更新一切如常。','Auto-updates for themes appear to be disabled. This will prevent your site from receiving new versions automatically when available.'=>'主题的自动更新似乎已被禁用。这将阻止您的网站自动接收可用的新版本。','Auto-updates for plugins appear to be disabled. This will prevent your site from receiving new versions automatically when available.'=>'插件的自动更新似乎已被禁用。这将阻止您的网站自动接收可用的新版本。','Auto-updates for plugins and themes appear to be disabled. This will prevent your site from receiving new versions automatically when available.'=>'插件和主题的自动更新似乎已被禁用。这将阻止您的网站自动接收可用的新版本。','Auto-updates for plugins and/or themes appear to be disabled, but settings are still set to be displayed. This could cause auto-updates to not work as expected.'=>'插件和（或）主题的自动更新似乎已被禁用，但是界面依然被设置为显示更新。这可能导致自动更新无法如期进行。','No scheduled events exist on this site.'=>'此站点不存在计划事件。','REST API availability'=>'REST API可用性','Authorization header'=>'授权标头','Loopback request'=>'环回请求','Background updates'=>'后台更新','Plugin and theme auto-updates'=>'插件和主题自动更新','Debugging enabled'=>'调试已启用','HTTP Requests'=>'HTTP请求','Scheduled events'=>'计划事件','Secure communication'=>'安全通信','HTTPS status'=>'HTTPS状态','MySQL utf8mb4 support'=>'MySQL utf8mb4支持','Database Server version'=>'数据库服务器版本','PHP Sessions'=>'PHP会话','PHP Default Timezone'=>'PHP默认时区','PHP Extensions'=>'PHP扩展','PHP Version'=>'PHP版本','Theme Versions'=>'主题版本','Plugin Versions'=>'插件版本','WordPress Version'=>'WordPress版本','Learn how to configure the Authorization header.'=>'了解如何配置授权标头。','https://developer.wordpress.org/rest-api/frequently-asked-questions/#why-is-authentication-not-working'=>'https://developer.wordpress.org/rest-api/frequently-asked-questions/#why-is-authentication-not-working','Flush permalinks'=>'重新整理固定链接','The authorization header is invalid.'=>'授权标头无效。','The authorization header is missing.'=>'授权标头丢失。','The Authorization header comes from the third-party applications you approve. Without it, those apps cannot connect to your site.'=>'授权标头来自您批准的第三方应用程序。如果没有授权标头，这些应用程序将无法连接到您的站点。','The Authorization header is working as expected.'=>'授权标头按预期工作。','The setting for %1$s is smaller than %2$s, this could cause some problems when trying to upload files.'=>'%1$s 的设定值小于%2$s，尝试上传文件时可能会导致一些问题。','The "%1$s" value is smaller than "%2$s".'=>'%1$s的值比%2$s小。','%1$s is set to %2$s. You won\'t be able to upload files on your site.'=>'%1$s的值被设置为%2$s，因此您无法在这个网站上传文件。','The %s function has been disabled, some media settings are unavailable because of this.'=>'%s函数已被禁用，因此某些媒体设置不可用。','The %1$s directive in %2$s determines if uploading files is allowed on your site.'=>'%2$s中的%1$s指令决定了您的网站是否允许上传文件。','Files can be uploaded.'=>'可以上传文件。','The REST API did not process the %s query parameter correctly.'=>'REST API未能正确处理%s请求参数。','The REST API did not behave correctly'=>'REST API行为不正确','The REST API call gave the following unexpected result: (%1$d) %2$s.'=>'REST API调用返回了预料之外的结果：（%1$d）%2$s。','The REST API encountered an unexpected result'=>'REST API遇到了预料之外的结果','Error: %1$s (%2$s)'=>'错误：%1$s（%2$s）','The REST API request failed due to an error.'=>'REST API请求因遇到了错误而失败。','The REST API encountered an error'=>'REST API遇到了错误','The REST API is one way WordPress, and other applications, communicate with the server. One example is the block editor screen, which relies on this to display, and save, your posts and pages.'=>'REST API是WordPress及其他应用与服务器通信的一种途径。例如区块编辑器页面，它依赖REST来显示及保存您的页面和文章。','The REST API is available'=>'REST API可用','HTTP requests have been blocked by the %1$s constant, with some allowed hosts: %2$s.'=>'HTTP请求已被%1$s常量阻止，并允许了一些主机：%2$s。','HTTP requests are partially blocked'=>'HTTP请求被部分阻止','HTTP requests have been blocked by the %s constant, with no allowed hosts.'=>'HTTP请求已被%s常量阻止，且没有允许的主机。','HTTP requests are blocked'=>'HTTP请求被阻止','It is possible for site maintainers to block all, or some, communication to other sites and services. If set up incorrectly, this may prevent plugins and themes from working as intended.'=>'站点维护者可以阻止全部或部分到其他站点和服务的连接。如果没有正确设置，这可能会让一些插件及主题停止工作。','HTTP requests seem to be working as expected'=>'HTTP请求似乎工作正常','Your site could not complete a loopback request'=>'您的站点不能完成环回请求','Loopback requests are used to run scheduled events, and are also used by the built-in editors for themes and plugins to verify code stability.'=>'环回请求被用来运行计划事件，也被内建的主题及插件编辑器使用来确保代码稳定性。','Your site can perform loopback requests'=>'您的站点可以进行环回请求','Your site may have problems auto-updating plugins and themes'=>'您的网站可能无法自动更新插件和主题','Plugin and theme auto-updates ensure that the latest versions are always installed.'=>'插件与主题的自动更新能保证安装的总是最新版本。','Plugin and theme auto-updates appear to be configured correctly'=>'插件和主题自动更新配置正确','Background updates may not be working properly'=>'后台更新可能未能正常工作','Background updates are not working as expected'=>'后台更新未能正常工作','Passed'=>'通过','Background updates ensure that WordPress can auto-update if a security update is released for the version you are currently using.'=>'后台更新确保WordPress能够在您正运行的版本需要安全更新时自动更新WordPress。','Background updates are working'=>'后台更新正常工作','The scheduled event, %s, is late to run. Your site still works, but this may indicate that scheduling posts or automated updates may not work as intended.'=>'计划事件%s执行被延迟。您的站点仍然工作，但这可能意味着定时发布或自动更新不再正常运行。','A scheduled event is late'=>'一个计划事件被延迟','The scheduled event, %s, failed to run. Your site still works, but this may indicate that scheduling posts or automated updates may not work as intended.'=>'计划事件%s执行失败。您的站点仍然工作，但这可能意味着定时发布或自动更新不再正常运行。','A scheduled event has failed'=>'一个计划事件已失败','While trying to test your site&#8217;s scheduled events, the following error was returned: %s'=>'在试图检查您的站点的计划事件时，遇到了此错误：%s','It was not possible to check your scheduled events'=>'不能检查您的计划事件','Scheduled events are what periodically looks for updates to plugins, themes and WordPress itself. It is also what makes sure scheduled posts are published on time. It may also be used by various plugins to make sure that planned actions are executed.'=>'计划事件包括定期检查插件、主题和WordPress自身的更新，也包括让计划文章按时发布。很多插件也通过计划事件来确保动作按期执行。','Scheduled events are running'=>'计划事件正在运行','Talk to your web host about OpenSSL support for PHP.'=>'请与您的主机提供商联系PHP的OpenSSL支持。','Your site is unable to communicate securely with other services'=>'您的站点不能与其他服务安全地通信','Your site can communicate securely with other services'=>'您的站点能够与其他服务安全地通信','Securely communicating between servers are needed for transactions such as fetching files, conducting sales on store sites, and much more.'=>'服务器间的安全通讯对传输文件、进行交易等活动而言实属必需。','Your site does not use HTTPS'=>'您的站点没有使用HTTPS','Update your site addresses'=>'更新您的站点地址','You are accessing this website using HTTPS, but your <a href="%s">WordPress Address</a> is not set up to use HTTPS by default.'=>'您正在通过HTTPS访问此网站，但您的<a href="%s">WordPress地址</a>并未默认使用HTTPS。','Only parts of your site are using HTTPS'=>'您的站点只有一部分使用HTTPS','Learn more about why you should use HTTPS'=>'了解关于为何您应该使用HTTPS的信息','https://wordpress.org/support/article/why-should-i-use-https/'=>'https://wordpress.org/support/article/why-should-i-use-https/','An HTTPS connection is a more secure way of browsing the web. Many services now have HTTPS as a requirement. HTTPS allows you to take advantage of new features that can increase site speed, improve search rankings, and gain the trust of your visitors by helping to protect their online privacy.'=>'HTTPS连接是更安全的网络浏览方式。许多服务都已开始要求使用HTTPS。HTTPS让您能够使用可以提高站点速度、改善搜索排名和通过保护访客隐私来赢得信任的新功能。','Your website is using an active HTTPS connection.'=>'您的站点正在使用活跃HTTPS连接。','The value, %1$s, has either been enabled by %2$s or added to your configuration file. This will make errors display on the front end of your site.'=>'此数值，%1$s，或是已被%2$s启用，或是已被加入您的配置文件。这将会让错误被显示在您的站点前端。','Your site is set to display errors to site visitors'=>'您的站点被设置为向站点访客展示错误','The value, %s, has been added to this website&#8217;s configuration file. This means any errors on the site will be written to a file which is potentially available to all users.'=>'数值%s已加入网站配置文件，这意味着此站点上发生的错误会被写入一个可能公开可见的文件。','Your site is set to log errors to a potentially public file.'=>'您的站点被设置为记录错误到一个可能公开的文件。','Debug mode is often enabled to gather more details about an error or site failure, but may contain sensitive information which should not be available on a publicly available website.'=>'调试模式通常被用来获得关于一个错误或站点功能的详细信息，但也可能包含在一个公开网站上不应泄露的敏感信息。','Your site is not set to output debug information'=>'您的站点没有被设置为输出调试信息','Get help resolving this issue.'=>'获取解决此问题的帮助。','https://wordpress.org/support'=>'https://cn.wordpress.org/support','Your site is unable to reach WordPress.org at %1$s, and returned the error: %2$s'=>'您的站点未能与WordPress.org（%1$s）通信，并返回了错误：%2$s','Could not reach WordPress.org'=>'未能与WordPress.org通信','Communicating with the WordPress servers is used to check for new versions, and to both install and update WordPress core, themes or plugins.'=>'WordPress需要联系服务器来检查最新版本和安装及更新WordPress核心、主题及插件。','Can communicate with WordPress.org'=>'能够与WordPress.org通信','WordPress&#8217; utf8mb4 support requires MySQL client library (%1$s) version %2$s or newer. Please contact your server administrator.'=>'WordPress的utf8mb4支持需要MySQL客户端库（%1$s）版本%2$s或更高。请联系您的服务器管理员。','utf8mb4 requires a newer client library'=>'utf8mb4需要更新的客户端库','Your MariaDB version supports utf8mb4.'=>'您的MariaDB版本支持utf8mb4。','WordPress&#8217; utf8mb4 support requires MariaDB version %s or greater. Please contact your server administrator.'=>'WordPress的utf8mb4支持需要MariaDB版本%s或更高。请联系您的服务器管理员。','utf8mb4 requires a MariaDB update'=>'utf8mb4需要MariaDB更新','Your MySQL version supports utf8mb4.'=>'您的MySQL版本支持utf8mb4。','WordPress&#8217; utf8mb4 support requires MySQL version %s or greater. Please contact your server administrator.'=>'WordPress的utf8mb4支持需要MySQL版本%s或更高。请联系您的服务器管理员。','utf8mb4 requires a MySQL update'=>'utf8mb4需要MySQL更新','UTF8MB4 is the character set WordPress prefers for database storage because it safely supports the widest set of characters and encodings, including Emoji, enabling better support for non-English languages.'=>'UTF8MB4是WordPress建议使用于数据库存储的字符集，它能安全地支持包括Emoji在内的字符和编码，并对非英文语言提供更好的支持。','UTF8MB4 is supported'=>'支持UTF8MB4','You are using a %1$s drop-in which might mean that a %2$s database is not being used.'=>'您正在使用增强插件%1$s，这可能意味着%2$s数据库并未被使用。','WordPress requires %1$s version %2$s or higher. Contact your web hosting company to correct this.'=>'WordPress需要%2$s及更高版本的%1$s。请联系您的主机提供商来修正此项。','Severely outdated SQL server'=>'极度陈旧的SQL服务器','For optimal performance and security reasons, we recommend running %1$s version %2$s or higher. Contact your web hosting company to correct this.'=>'出于性能和安